    "File13 Pro" : {

    },
    "File13 sends headers only — never message bodies — to your configured AI provider when this runs." : {

    },
    "File13 uses AI for inbox triage on headers only (e.g., sender, subject, date). Body content is never read or sent. Choose Apple's on-device model for the strongest privacy; choose a third-party provider for more flexibility." : {

    },
    "File13 uses the sender's List-Unsubscribe header. One-click links unsubscribe in place; web links open in your browser. The sender may identify you from the URL." : {
